Text.valUnicode: NOTE:- FOR NOT RECEIVED AND NG TAGS REFER ORIGINATOR REPORT

ItemsList.valUnicode: 1: All Data For All Division,2: Division And Duration Both,3: Division Only,4: Duration Only

ExpSyntax.val: 'Please select option 2 or 3 only in case of originator !!!'
'IPP TAG STATUS REPORT'&' '&'('&IF ({1,3}='1','All Data For All Division',IF ({1,3}='2','Division And Duration Both',IF ({1,3}='3','Division Only','Duration Only')))&')'

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT * FROM IPPTAGHDR H, IPPTAGDTL D WHERE H.CONTROLNO=D.CONTROLNO and D.STATUS='P' and H.RECUPDATEDATE='00000000' AND H.ORIGINATOR = :1 and h.initdate>= :2 and h.initdate <=:3 AND NOT EXISTS (select C.controlno from IPPTAGDTL c where c.status<>'P' and c.controlno= D.controlno)

ExpSyntax.val: 'IPP TAG STATUS REPORT'&' '&'('&IF ({1,3}='1','All Data For All Division',IF ({1,3}='2','Division And Duration Both',IF ({1,3}='3','Division Only','Duration Only')))&')'

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT * FROM IPPTAGHDR H, IPPTAGDTL D WHERE H.CONTROLNO=D.CONTROLNO and D.STATUS='J' AND H.ORIGINATOR = :1 AND H.RECUPDATEDATE >= ':2' AND H.RECUPDATEDATE <= ':3' AND EXISTS (select C.controlno from IPPTAGDTL c where c.status<>'J' and c.controlno= D.controlno)

ExpSyntax.val: 'IPP TAG STATUS REPORT'&' '&'('&IF ({1,3}='1','All Data For All Division',IF ({1,3}='2','Division And Duration Both',IF ({1,3}='3','Division Only','Duration Only')))&')'
